## Performance Best Practices

### Async/Await

```csharp
// Good
public async Task<ProcessResult> Handle(SuscripcionCreada @event, CancellationToken ct)
{
    var exists = await _repository.GetByIdAsync(@event.Id);
    return new ProcessResult { Succed = true };
}

// Avoid blocking
public ProcessResult Handle(SuscripcionCreada @event, CancellationToken ct)
{
    var exists = _repository.GetByIdAsync(@event.Id).Result;  // ❌
}
```

### Database Query Optimization

```csharp
// Good: Check existence without loading entity
const string sql = "SELECT COUNT(1) FROM Suscripciones WHERE Id = @Id";
var exists = await _context.Connection.ExecuteScalarAsync<int>(sql, new { Id = id }) > 0;

// Avoid: Loading full entity just to check existence
var entity = await _repository.GetByIdAsync(id);  // ❌
var exists = entity != null;
```

