### HU Cleanup (Mandatory)

After completing the implementation, building tests, and ensuring full compilation, perform a final audit to detect and eliminate any code, configuration, or boilerplate not directly related to the Current User Story (HU).
- Remove unused template files (`MessageProcessor.cs`, `Customer.cs`, etc.)
- Remove unrelated API infrastructure from worker projects (CORS, Swagger, Auth if not used).
- Clean up `global usings` and generic utilities that are not required for the specific business logic.

